sql_query.sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS count_all, date(users.created_at) AS date_users_created_at FROM "users" WHERE (users.id > 0) AND (NOT EXISTS(
                     SELECT 1
                     FROM anonymous_users a
                     WHERE a.user_id = users.id
                  )) AND (users.created_at >= '2020-05-27 00:00:00' AND users.created_at <= '2020-06-26 23:59:59.999999') GROUP BY date(users.created_at) ORDER BY date(users.created_at)
